Telefonica UK Limited, [[trading as]] O2 UK (stylised as O₂), is a British [[List of telephone operating companies#United Kingdom|telecommunications services provider]], headquartered in [[Slough]], England which operates under the [[O2 (brand)|O2 brand]].<ref>Contact us, O₂ corporate website. Retrieved: 6 December 2012.</ref> It is owned by [[Virgin Media O2|VMED O2 UK Limited]], a 50:50 joint venture between [[Telefónica]] and [[Liberty Global]]. O2 is the UK's [[List of mobile network operators of Europe#United Kingdom|largest mobile network operator]], with 23.8 million subscribers as of May 2023.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.telefonica.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2023/02/rdos23t1-data.xlsx |title=2023 Quarterly Results - Telefónica |date=10 May 2023 |publisher=Telefónica}}</ref>

